	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Fri, Jun 7th 4:23 PM 2002</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[2.60]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Hello, I am Alloran a 12th level bard. I was always aware of Dex helping your songs procs and stuff but I really had never been a seeker of dex wiht my shadowknight or druid. I also understand the importance of AC through my SK as a tank. I don't really know of any ac/dex items out there wiht a good combo of both. Help me out please! If dex is so important to bards but is it more important than AC? Thanks all<br><br>Islude-&quot;From the south. Heh, the deep south.&quot;<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
