	   <tr><td colspan=2>well actually i think that the reason you never see a bard with a 2 handed weapon is simply because they don't get 2 hand slash or 2 hand bunt, which are separate skills to their one handed counterparts. Piercing on the other hand is a single skill that covers both 1 handed and 2 handed weapons. There are only about 20 2 handed pierce weapons in the whole game, and this spear is the first i've seen that includes bard as a usuable class. It also includes shamman, and they do get one other 2hp, the spirit talkers war lance (that big lance thing they like to show off). Now i don't have a bard character to test yet, but I have used it on my ranger (they have no 2 hand pierce usable weapons either except for this) and it works, so maybe this is just the first 2 hand piercer a bard or ranger can use. If shammy's always had just the one 2hp weapon available to them there's no reason why bard's and rangers can't have just the one available. <br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Fri Jun&nbsp;&nbsp;7 13:24:55 2002</em><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
