	   <tr><td colspan=2>In my experience as a bard, I never needed the f1-f8 keys to target party members.&nbsp;&nbsp;Instead remap these to the spell gems and use f1-f8 to cast. Very fast, very efficient. Frees the mouse for targeting dots, etc. (move the target party to at f1-8 if you like)<br><br>You can go farter and us page up to target u (or hit twice for pet) and page down for target nearest npc.<br>&nbsp;<br>Baron Nesoohc Tsal, the Rathe<br>Bard of the 53nd Song<br><br>Bhandade 11th season Cleric...FV<br>'TOTALLY' untwinked</td></tr>
